description: Kona Ice of Sienna is serving up the shaved ice that's oh-so-nice on the streets of Texas.Quality frozen treats aren't hard to come by these days, so what sets Kona Ice apart? It's a dedication to friendly service and fun times. Each and every event that Kona Ice comes to is sure to be a phenomenally good time that you're sure to love.Experience a tropical treat today, with the amazing Kona Ice!
name: Kona Ice of Sienna
